===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ˈæft.ɚˈnuːn/

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

#{{time}}: The part of the [[day]] which follows [[noon]], between noon and [[evening]].
# The part of the day following noon which is daylight all year round; the second half of the working day (in regular office hours).
